select #time#, nvl("rnc".co_name, nvl("rnc".co_object_instance, 'NN('||"rnc".co_gid||')')) "RNC name", nvl("wbts".co_name, nvl("wbts".co_object_instance, 'NN('||"wbts".co_gid||')')) "WBTS name", #keys#, #kpis# from utp_common_objects "rnc", utp_common_objects "wbts" #tmp_meas_tables# where "wbts".co_parent_gid = "rnc".co_gid and #first_tmp_table#.wbts_gid = "wbts".co_gid #tmp_table_joins# #add_on_criteria# order by #add_on_sort#

select #time#, nvl("rnc".co_name, nvl("rnc".co_object_instance, 'NN('||"rnc".co_gid||')')) "RNC name", nvl("wbts".co_name, nvl("wbts".co_object_instance, 'NN('||"wbts".co_gid||')')) "WBTS name", nvl("wcel".co_name, nvl("wcel".co_object_instance, 'NN('||"wcel".co_gid||')')) "WCEL name", #keys#, #kpis# from utp_common_objects "rnc", utp_common_objects "wbts", utp_common_objects "wcel" #tmp_meas_tables# where "wbts".co_parent_gid = "rnc".co_gid and "wcel".co_parent_gid = "wbts".co_gid and #first_tmp_table#.wcel_gid = "wcel".co_gid #tmp_table_joins# #add_on_criteria# order by #add_on_sort#

select #id_pivot#, decode(nvl(mr.co_name, nvl(mr.co_object_instance, 'NN ('||mr.co_gid||')')),' ','NN ('||mr.co_gid||')',nvl(mr.co_name, nvl(mr.co_object_instance, 'NN ('||mr.co_gid||')'))) "MR Name", #kpis# from utp_common_objects mr #tmp_meas_tables# where mr.co_oc_id=109 and #first_tmp_table#.mr_gid = mr.co_gid #tmp_table_joins# #add_on_criteria# order by 2,1,3
select #id_pivot#, 1 WS_DUMMY, #kpis# from dual #tmp_meas_tables# where 1=1 #tmp_table_joins# #add_on_criteria# order by #add_on_sort#
